<a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/chiara-fracasso/" rel="tag">Chiara Fracasso</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/fabrizio-beggi/" rel="tag">Fabrizio Beggi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/federico-longhi/" rel="tag">Federico Longhi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/franco-rizzo/" rel="tag">Franco Rizzo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gabriele-sagona/" rel="tag">Gabriele Sagona</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gianluigi-gelmetti/" rel="tag">Gianluigi gelmetti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giovanna-lanza/" rel="tag">Giovanna Lanza</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lamberto-puggelli/" rel="tag">Lamberto Puggelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/luca-casalin/" rel="tag">Luca Casalin</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/luisa-spinatelli/" rel="tag">Luisa Spinatelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marcelo-alvarez/" rel="tag">Marcelo Alvarez</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/maria-jose-siri/" rel="tag">Maria Josè Siri</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/matteo-peirone/" rel="tag">Matteo Peirone</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica-teatro-regio-di-torino/" rel="tag">Opera lirica. Teatro Regio di Torino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/paolo-bregni/" rel="tag">Paolo Bregni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/renato-palumbo/" rel="tag">Renato Palumbo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/scott-johnson/" rel="tag">Scott Johnson</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/umberto-giordano/" rel="tag">Umberto Giordano</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alberto Mastromarino, Andrea Chénier, Chiara Fracasso, Fabrizio Beggi, Federico Longhi, Franco Rizzo, Gabriele Sagona, Gianluigi gelmetti, Giovanna Lanza, Lamberto Puggelli, Luca Casalin, Luisa Spinatelli, Marcelo Alvarez, Maria Josè Siri, Matteo Peirone, Opera lirica. Teatro Regio di Torino, Paolo Bregni, Renato Palumbo, Scott Johnson, Umberto Giordano"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/dallanime-esultanti-sboccia-lamor-la-boheme-al-teatro-regio-di-torino/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> «Dall’anime esultanti / sboccia l’amor».  La bohème al Teatro Regio di Torino</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/02/intervista-a-luca-dallamico/" rel="next">Intervista a Luca Dall&#8217;Amico <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/02/il-nostro-e-amore-danime-andrea-chenier-al-teatro-regio-di-torino/#res